<PAGE width="419.64" height="595.32" number="214" id="p214"><MEDIABOX x1="0" y1="0" x2="419.64" y2="595.32"/><CROPBOX x1="0" y1="0" x2="419.64" y2="595.32"/><BLEEDBOX x1="0" y1="0" x2="419.64" y2="595.32"/><ARTBOX x1="0" y1="0" x2="419.64" y2="595.32"/><TRIMBOX x1="0" y1="0" x2="419.64" y2="595.32"/><TEXT width="12.7715" height="7.668" id="p214_t1" x="203.45" y="569.101"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21134" id="p214_w1" font-name="Times New Roman" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="8.52" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="203.45" y="569.101" base="574.92" width="12.7715" height="7.668">214</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="316.092" height="9" id="p214_t2" x="56.424" y="46.08"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21137" id="p214_w2" font-name="IPA¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="46.08" base="54" width="316.092" height="9">水といっても日本と違ってぬるま湯が出てくるのが面白い。ゕルテゖガ教では体を冷や</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="237.129" height="9" id="p214_t3" x="48.264" y="63.02"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21138" id="p214_w3" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="63.02" base="70.94" width="237.129" height="9">すことは良くないとされるため、冷水は好まれないのだそうだ。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="316.101" height="9" id="p214_t4" x="56.424" y="80.06"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21141" id="p214_w4" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="80.06" base="87.98" width="316.101" height="9">軟水が多いので、料理も西洋料理とはところどころで異なる。うどんやそばもある。そ</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="131.166" height="9" id="p214_t5" x="48.264" y="97.1"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21142" id="p214_w5" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="97.1" base="105.02" width="131.166" height="9">ば好きの私としては嬉しい限りだ。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="204.606" height="9" id="p214_t6" x="56.424" y="131.06"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21146" id="p214_w6" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="131.06" base="138.98" width="204.606" height="9">暇を持て余し、ぼーっとヴゔルデの入った袋を見やる。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="147.486" height="9" id="p214_t7" x="56.424" y="148.1"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21149" id="p214_w7" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="148.1" base="156.02" width="147.486" height="9">こんな杖が神の武器だったなんてねぇ。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="316.092" height="9" id="p214_t8" x="56.424" y="165.05"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21152" id="p214_w8" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="165.05" base="172.97" width="316.092" height="9">それにしてもいいんだろうか。だってほら、私あれでネブラに刺し面しちゃったし。小</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="90.6" height="9" id="p214_t9" x="48.264" y="182.09"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21153" id="p214_w9" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="182.09" base="190.01" width="90.6" height="9">手も打っちゃったわよ。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="253.332" height="9" id="p214_t10" x="56.424" y="199.13"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21156" id="p214_w10" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="199.13" base="207.05" width="253.332" height="9">神話のゕ゗テムを竹刀代わりにしてしまった。バゴが当たりそうだ。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="316.092" height="9" id="p214_t11" x="56.424" y="233.09"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21160" id="p214_w11" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="233.09" base="241.01" width="316.092" height="9">私は情報を整理するために神話で読んだ知識を思い起こした。固有名詞ばかりなので誰</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="285.972" height="9" id="p214_t12" x="48.264" y="250.13"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21161" id="p214_w12" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="250.13" base="258.05" width="285.972" height="9">が誰だか覚えづらい。何度か頭の中で想起して定着させないと忘れてしまう。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="314.566" height="9.873" id="p214_t13" x="56.424" y="267.05"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21164" id="p214_w13" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="267.05" base="274.97" width="245.172" height="9">ヴゔルデの最初の持ち主はゕルデガ王の父親だった。ゕルミヴゔの</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p214_s21165" id="p214_w14" font-name="times new roman" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="302.95" y="268.823" base="274.97" width="8.58" height="8.1">12</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p214_s21166" id="p214_w15" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="313.03" y="267.05" base="274.97" width="57.96" height="9">神でもある竜王</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="202.559" height="9" id="p214_t14" x="48.264" y="284.11"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21167" id="p214_w16" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="284.11" base="292.03" width="53.46" height="9">テゖアノだ。9</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p214_s21168" id="p214_w17" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="103.22" y="284.11" base="292.03" width="147.603" height="9">時の人といえば分かりやすいだろうか。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="316.159" height="9" id="p214_t15" x="56.424" y="301.15"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21171" id="p214_w18" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="301.15" base="309.07" width="204.649" height="9">ゕオ゚ットのリデゖゕはこの杖を借りて悪魔と戦った。</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p214_s21172" id="p214_w19" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="257.59" y="301.15" base="309.07" width="114.993" height="9">その後リデゖゕが杖を返納して</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="90.6" height="9" id="p214_t16" x="48.264" y="318.07"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21173" id="p214_w20" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="318.07" base="325.99" width="90.6" height="9">一旦は神の手に戻った。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="315.975" height="9" id="p214_t17" x="56.424" y="335.11"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21176" id="p214_w21" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="335.11" base="343.03" width="315.975" height="9">しかし今回月の悪魔オ゚ルテガがゕルデガ王の息子ト゘ッテゖを襲い、ヴゔルデはゕル</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="74.28" height="9" id="p214_t18" x="48.264" y="352.15"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21177" id="p214_w22" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="352.15" base="360.07" width="74.28" height="9">バォードに落ちた。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="237.129" height="9" id="p214_t19" x="56.424" y="369.07"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21180" id="p214_w23" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="369.07" base="376.99" width="237.129" height="9">そして今現在は私の手に握られている。なんとも不思議な話だ。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="204.626" height="9" id="p214_t20" x="56.424" y="386.11"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21183" id="p214_w24" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="386.11" base="394.03" width="204.626" height="9">月の悪魔オ゚ルテガ、魔杖ヴゔルデ、人工言語ゕルゞ。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="163.806" height="9" id="p214_t21" x="56.424" y="403.18"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21186" id="p214_w25" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="403.18" base="411.1" width="163.806" height="9">この世界は不思議なもので満ち溢れている。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="131.186" height="9" id="p214_t22" x="48.264" y="420.1"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21188" id="p214_w26" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="420.1" base="428.02" width="131.186" height="9">「月と魔法と不思議な言葉……か」</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="316.152" height="9" id="p214_t23" x="56.424" y="471.1"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21193" id="p214_w27" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="471.1" base="479.02" width="316.152" height="9">窓の外を見る。地下を走るのは都市部だけなので、田舎だと電車は地上を走る。田園風</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="98.76" height="9" id="p214_t24" x="48.264" y="488.136"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21194" id="p214_w28" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="488.136" base="496.056" width="98.76" height="9">景が視界に広がっている。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="316.028" height="9" id="p214_t25" x="56.424" y="505.2"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21197" id="p214_w29" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="505.2" base="513.12" width="316.028" height="9">ゞテーカュってどんなところなんだろう。ド゘ルゟさんとは会えるのだろうか。彼は魔</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="123.123" height="9" id="p214_t26" x="48.264" y="522.12"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21198" id="p214_w30" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="522.12" base="530.04" width="123.123" height="9">法をどの程度使えるのだろうか。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="98.636" height="9" id="p214_t27" x="56.424" y="539.16"><TOKEN sid="p214_s21201" id="p214_w31" font-name="ipa¾©" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="539.16" base="547.08" width="98.636" height="9">見てみたいなぁ……魔法。</TOKEN></TEXT></PAGE>
